asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: Nero
description: I'm back! Some think I'm a slight mad man, but you can't blame me. Have you tried to get your head around the fact that your body is decaying? Try thinking positive about that, it's pretty hard. I like to blow my whistle and wear a clown nose to remind myself of the good times we can still have even when we are not our complete selves. I mean, I admit it, I'm not at my best, but hey at least I still have a consciousness of some sort. Still trying to figure out what to do with my inverted purple ring eyes. Someone told me that if I try hard enough they do something super cool. Let me know if you can help? Love you little fluffers!

name: Jack Bun Tai AKA Jungle Boogie
description: Jack Bun Tai, code name "Jungle Boogie", is Field Marshal of the DFU (Decentralized FLUF Unit), a paramilitary organisation who are sworn to protect locations where the Underground connects with the rest of society. He usually operates from a secret location in Asia but he maintains extensive local and international connections through his cover work as a resident techno DJ at a world-famous Island Jungle Party. While many assume his halo is just a holographic accessory for his DJ act, it appeared after a near death experience at the Battle for London. His unit had been assigned to investigate the source of unusual levels of gas discovered at many entrances to the Underground. After narrowing down their search to a mysterious figure in a fox mask, his team were ambushed in an infamous series of gas attacks now known as "The Drops".  The full details of the Battle for London are still classified but it is understood that Jungle Boogie awoke in a swamp a few days later with a Halo floating above his head and broken memories of encountering the mysterious fox-masked figure before climbing a stairway leading to a gate in the clouds. It's rumoured that Jungle Boogie and the DFU are now heavily involved in another mission for the Fluffle, one known only as "Operation Merge  Shard". In the meantime, if you know where to find him, you can still catch him spinning the decks one day before every full moon to a neon crowd literally shaking with good vibes.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
